<p>The <code>TaskListItem</code> represents one step in a
  <a href="/components/task-list/"><code>TaskList</code></a>. The
  <code>status</code> param controls the visual state:
  <code>completed</code>, <code>in-progress</code>,
  <code>not-started</code>, or <code>cannot-start-yet</code>.</p>

<p>See the <a href="/components/task-list/">TaskList demo</a> for
  the composed example.</p>
